Coba kasih senyuman manis.

516
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:17,400
Siap.

517
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:20,650
Kalau fotografernya dia, apa pun aku mau.

518
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:27,050
Lanjut, dek.

519
00:35:29,890 --> 00:35:31,030
Oke.

520
00:35:31,690 --> 00:35:34,880
Bagus, selesai. Semuanya sempurna.

521
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:37,220
Syutingnya selesai.

522
00:35:37,220 --> 00:35:39,220
Kamu boleh istirahat sekarang.

523
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:41,220
Yang berikut, siap-siap.

524
00:35:43,130 --> 00:35:45,060
Kalian ngapain ke sini?

525
00:35:45,900 --> 00:35:48,720
Kenapa? Nggak boleh?

526
00:35:48,720 --> 00:35:51,240
Kami cuma mau lihat kamu kok.

527
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,800
Tadi juga dengar hal lucu, lho.

528
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:55,440
"Kalau fotografernya dia,"

529
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:57,440
"apa pun aku mau."

530
00:35:59,180 --> 00:36:03,770
Orang yang kamu maksud itu ya?

531
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:06,160
Iya.

532
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:09,710
Pasti sulit menaklukkannya.

533
00:36:10,910 --> 00:36:11,900
Kenapa?

534
00:36:11,900 --> 00:36:13,150
Lihat saja.

535
00:36:13,150 --> 00:36:16,510
"Soalnya pemilik jam tangan itu sudah lepas jamnya."

536
00:36:16,510 --> 00:36:18,510
Iya juga ya.

537
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:20,390
Kamu jahat banget.

538
00:36:20,390 --> 00:36:23,070
Mungkin cuma lupa pakai.

539
00:36:26,050 --> 00:36:29,150
Aku sungguh mendukungmu, bro!

540
00:36:29,650 --> 00:36:30,520
Iya.

541
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:35,020
Ayo istirahat, biar fotografernya minum sebentar.

542
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:39,560
Ayo istirahat di sebelah.

543
00:36:44,370 --> 00:36:45,890
Pokoknya,

544
00:36:45,890 --> 00:36:48,060
aku mau kenalan sama dia.

545
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:49,130
Jangan.

546
00:36:49,130 --> 00:36:51,130
Hei, Arthit.

547
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:53,130
Jo

548
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:56,950
Kamu harus ikut lihat juga.

549
00:36:56,950 --> 00:36:58,950
Mereka mungkin akan bikin masalah.

550
00:37:11,820 --> 00:37:13,360
Halo, adik Ter.

551
00:37:14,710 --> 00:37:16,060
Halo, Johan.

552
00:37:16,060 --> 00:37:19,100
Aku Arthit, temannya Hill.

553
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:21,180
Halo, Arthit.

554
00:37:22,650 --> 00:37:24,150
Kalian sedang bicara apa?

555
00:37:25,170 --> 00:37:26,590
Halo, Anak Paskah.

556
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:30,350
Namaku Tonfha, senang bertemu denganmu.

557
00:37:30,350 --> 00:37:31,650
Halo.

558
00:37:31,650 --> 00:37:33,170
Aku Anak Paskah.

559
00:37:33,170 --> 00:37:34,730
Panggil saja aku Ter.

560
00:37:34,730 --> 00:37:36,490
Aku mahasiswa kedokteran hewan tahun pertama.

561
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:37,960
Oh, mahasiswa baru kedokteran hewan.

562
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:40,360
Fakultasmu dekat dengan fakultasku.

563
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:44,730
Setahuku, dulu kalian juga pakai lab kami.

564
00:37:45,590 --> 00:37:47,690
Mungkin kita akan sering bertemu.

565
00:37:49,130 --> 00:37:50,690
Sudah kenalan, bisa pergi kan?

566
00:37:50,690 --> 00:37:53,700
Eh, kenapa ada aroma cemburu ya?

567
00:37:54,520 --> 00:37:57,920
Baru kenalan kok, belum ngobrol serius.

568
00:37:57,920 --> 00:37:59,710
Adik Ter.

569
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:01,990
Tolong jaga temanku baik-baik.

570
00:38:01,990 --> 00:38:05,880
Walau tidak suka, tetap perlakukan dia baik.

571
00:38:06,320 --> 00:38:09,710
Karena dia bukan tipe yang mudah jatuh cinta.

572
00:38:13,010 --> 00:38:14,580
Kalian pergilah.

573
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:18,000
Abaikan saja mereka.

574
00:38:22,860 --> 00:38:23,840
Ter.

575
00:38:25,060 --> 00:38:26,090
Apa?

576
00:38:27,090 --> 00:38:28,800
Aku ingin bicara sesuatu denganmu.

577
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:34,060
Oke.

578
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:44,040
Terima kasih.

579
00:38:49,810 --> 00:38:51,400
Ayo kita pergi.

580
00:38:52,540 --> 00:38:53,770
Aku pergi dulu ya.

581
00:38:55,580 --> 00:38:56,990
"Ter,"

582
00:38:56,990 --> 00:38:58,990
"Aku ingin bicara sesuatu."

583
00:39:12,870 --> 00:39:14,870
Hill, kau mau bilang sesuatu?

584
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:23,430
Aku nggak tahu harus mulai dari mana.

585
00:39:27,670 --> 00:39:29,610
Aku cuma ingin mulai dari awal lagi.

586
00:39:34,660 --> 00:39:35,930
Aku rasa...

587
00:39:35,930 --> 00:39:38,040
Kita sudah berusaha lari dari masa lalu.

588
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:41,050
Aku rasa kita harus bicara jelas.

589
00:39:41,050 --> 00:39:43,050
Bersikap seolah masa lalu tak ada itu buruk.

590
00:39:52,130 --> 00:39:54,780
Kau mau tanya apa padaku?

591
00:39:59,460 --> 00:40:01,300
Apa pun boleh ditanya?

592
00:40:03,190 --> 00:40:05,660
Aku akan jawab semua pertanyaanmu.

593
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:09,390
Seberapa jauh aku bisa percaya padamu?

594
00:40:09,390 --> 00:40:11,390
Seratus persen.

595
00:40:13,720 --> 00:40:15,090
Kalau begitu...

596
00:40:15,520 --> 00:40:17,970
Bagaimana aku tahu kau tidak bohong?

597
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:21,590
Akan kubuktikan.

598
00:40:30,750 --> 00:40:33,870
Pertanyaan pertamaku...

599
00:40:35,830 --> 00:40:37,220
Ya?

600
00:40:37,540 --> 00:40:41,110
Kau dan Thunmild...

601
00:40:43,630 --> 00:40:45,330
Kenapa?

602
00:40:46,340 --> 00:40:48,570
Apa hubungan kalian?

603
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:51,450
Kami cuma teman.

604
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:53,140
Oh.

605
00:40:57,090 --> 00:40:58,790
Kalian nggak pacaran?

606
00:40:59,460 --> 00:41:01,620
Kupikir kalian sedang dekat.

607
00:41:01,620 --> 00:41:04,120
Bagiku, Thunmild hanya teman.

608
00:41:08,050 --> 00:41:09,110
Serius?

609
00:41:21,780 --> 00:41:22,810
Dan...

610
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:26,700
Dan...

611
00:41:27,830 --> 00:41:29,240
Bagaimana dengan Anak Natal?

612
00:41:30,610 --> 00:41:32,140
Aku anggap dia adik.

613
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:36,030
Tapi...

614
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:39,030
Tapi kau dan...

615
00:41:46,300 --> 00:41:49,300
Kupikir kau suka Anak Natal.

616
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:51,640
Aku tak pernah anggap dia seperti itu.

617
00:42:12,660 --> 00:42:13,700
Dan...

618
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:15,700
Kalau aku?

619
00:42:19,580 --> 00:42:20,820
Hmm?

620
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:22,820
Kenapa?

621
00:42:23,480 --> 00:42:26,010
Kalau aku gimana?

622
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:29,920
Kau sudah tahu jawabannya.

623
00:42:31,860 --> 00:42:33,530
Apa maksudmu sudah tahu?

624
00:42:37,110 --> 00:42:39,140
Kalau aku ingin bersama seseorang...

625
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:41,770
Itu pasti cuma satu alasannya, kan?

626
00:42:43,750 --> 00:42:48,410
Alasan satu-satunya itu...

627
00:42:48,850 --> 00:42:51,120
"Perasaan itu", benar?

628
00:42:54,390 --> 00:42:55,670
Kalau...

629
00:42:56,010 --> 00:43:00,220
Maksudmu "aku suka kamu", kan?

630
00:43:01,820 --> 00:43:02,850
Ya.

631
00:43:04,090 --> 00:43:04,870
Ah.

632
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:07,150
Sejak kapan itu?

633
00:43:08,920 --> 00:43:10,200
Maksudnya?

634
00:43:10,720 --> 00:43:14,430
Sejak kapan kau suka aku?

635
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:18,890
Mungkin sebelum kau kenal aku.

636
00:43:22,080 --> 00:43:23,070
Hah?

637
00:43:23,830 --> 00:43:25,800
Kau tak percaya?

638
00:43:27,420 --> 00:43:28,960
Mana mungkin?

639
00:43:32,700 --> 00:43:36,570
Soalnya aku sudah...

640
00:43:40,850 --> 00:43:42,550
Apa tadi?

641
00:43:51,720 --> 00:43:53,930
Karena aku sudah lama naksir kamu.

642
00:44:00,640 --> 00:44:02,060
Tak selama aku naksir kamu.

643
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:49,870
(Minggu depan) Bisakah kau jenguk dia?

644
00:44:49,870 --> 00:44:51,870
(Minggu depan) Akan kau lihat sesuatu yang keren.

645
00:44:55,640 --> 00:44:57,770
Ini orang yang ingin kau pacari?

646
00:44:57,770 --> 00:44:59,770
Ya.

647
00:44:59,770 --> 00:45:02,170
Apa aku kalah dari dia? Kenapa bukan aku?

648
00:45:02,760 --> 00:45:05,620
Saat mabuk, kau bisa lakukan apa saja.

649
00:45:05,620 --> 00:45:07,470
Jadi Hill nggak perlu buang waktu denganmu.

650
00:45:07,470 --> 00:45:09,500
Buang waktu?

651
00:45:09,500 --> 00:45:13,450
Kupikir kau tidak akan angkat teleponku lagi.

